    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Tomassino, a skeleton writer, on a thrilling adventure full of mystery! Explore haunted Match 3 boards as he unravels the secrets of a sorrowful family. Banish spooky creatures using magical light talismans, solve puzzles, enjoy fun minigames, and discover all the exciting features this game offers. Create a 3D Halloween-themed playground filled with spooky buildings and objects. You'll guide a group of eerie characters from a portal, helping them find homes in your playground. Will you and Tomassino succeed, or will the shadows win?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >150 Match 3 levels to conquer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and customize your 3D Otherworldly Playground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead Spooky Dwellers to lurk in houses in your Otherworldly Playground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Objects and other minigames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect trophies for more coins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wallpapers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extra stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal and Expert Match 3 modes.</p>",
